+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:415
+msgid "...my lord!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Relgorn
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:419
+msgid "Do not worry, young Hamel, I am sure Knalga will be fine in your capable hands. You'll be more than up to the job. And besides, you'll have Aiglathing and Dulatus to help you!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Aiglathing
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:423
+msgid "That's right."
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Dulatus
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:427
+msgid "Indeed."
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=Clarissa
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:434
+msgid "Don't forget about us!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=Celylia
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:439
+msgid "Your elf allies will be available for whenever you need us!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=Pelcatlus
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:444
+msgid "Call on me, if you ever need someone to crack the skulls of a few more baddies!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=Krolock
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:449
+msgid "Krolock help, too!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=Elara
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:454
+msgid "Feel free to call on me whenever you are in need of human magic!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=Hamel
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:458
+msgid "Wow, everyone... I don't know what to say! Thank you all very much, from the bottom of my heart."
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Relgorn
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:468
+msgid "Anyways, I am very tired now, so please excuse me while I retire to my chambers."
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Hamel
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:490
+msgid "All right, now that I'm in command... well, let's assemble all my forces first to hear my first decree!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Hamel
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:495
+msgid "All right, now that everyone's here... I guess my first decree should be to find that book of Thursagan's that explains the runelore required to use that hammer!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Hamel
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:517
+msgid "...actually, I guess we probably should have done that before sending the hammer off to Karrag in Kal Kartha... oops... oh well..."
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Aiglathing
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:521
+msgid "We shall continue to search for this book nonetheless, Lord Hamel!"
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: id=Dulatus
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:525
+msgid "Indeed, we shall."
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=narrator
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:547
+msgid "Hamel's rule of Knalga for the next few years was relatively uneventful, until 534 YW, when he became involved in the events portrayed in the campaign 'Northern Rebirth'."
+msgstr ""
+
+#. [message]: speaker=narrator
+#. A bit of a reference to the campaign's title here, but I'm not doing it word-for-word because "The Earth's Gut"
+#. would sound more awkward than "the gut of the earth" here:
+#: The_Earths_Gut/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:554
+msgid "And thus ends the tale of Hamel's journey into the gut of the earth at Kal Torlat, and his ascension to Lord of Knalga."
+msgstr ""
